        <item>
            <title>
                <![CDATA[Circle、全家便利商店与币托集团合作，新版「点数换币」超商可换 USDC]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>面对 2024 年比特币减半以及下轮加密牛市，币托集团 (BitoGroup) 旗下 BitoPro 加密货币交易所、全家便利商店、稳定币 USDC 发行商 Circle，携手推出新版本「点数换币」主动出击，搭配全新 BitoPro 币托交易所 App，大幅度降低民众从 Web2 到 Web3 的入圈门槛，此次跨圈合作可望为三方带来会员跨圈效应，持续强化 Web3 基础建设。</p><p>币托集团创办人暨执行长郑光泰表示：「便利商店点数深入台湾民众的日常生活，币托持续升级点数兑换虚币服务，降低大众进入 Web3 门槛。对于点数发行商来说，此点数换币的商业模式更能吸引新族群、刺激消费，甚至提升顾客黏著度，活络点数应用场景。币托对于通路伙伴合作保持开放精神，希望能携手更多合作伙伴前进 Web3。币托集团致力于成为企业与大众从 Web2 跨足 Web3 的第一哩路，目前拥有 80 万会员，目标 2023 年突破 100 万大关。」</p><p><img class="alignnone wp-image-81701 size-full" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/circle-scaled.jpeg?resize=2560%2C1675&amp;ssl=1" alt="circle" width="2560" height="1675" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/circle-scaled.jpeg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/circle-scaled.jpeg?resize=300%2C196&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/circle-scaled.jpeg?resize=1024%2C670&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/circle-scaled.jpeg?resize=600%2C393&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/circle-scaled.jpeg?resize=768%2C503&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/circle-scaled.jpeg?resize=1536%2C1005&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/circle-scaled.jpeg?resize=2048%2C1340&amp;ssl=1 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_57 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">内容目录</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/circle-bitopro-family-partnered-on-points-to-token-service#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-653a6a1fb284b"><span cla