                <![CDATA[<p class="intro_quote">Uniswap 为防范代码抄袭引入 BSL 商业许可证，dYdX Chain 则宣布代码完全开源；Uniswap 要收 0.15% 的前端手续费，dYdX 则宣布转型公共利益公司，不会从 V4 产生任何交易收入。两者的发展似乎有火药味。</p><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_57 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">内容目录</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/dydx-chain-v10-released#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-653a6a1fbabab"><span class=""><span style="display:none;">Toggle</span><span class="ez-toc-icon-toggle-span"><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="list-377408" width="20px" height="20px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999" class="arrow-unsorted-368013"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="10px" height="10px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.2" baseProfile="tiny"><path d="M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z"></path></svg></span></span></label><input aria-label="Toggle" type="checkbox" id="item-653a6a1fbabab"></a></span></div><nav><ul class="ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 "><li class="insert-page-1 insert-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1" href="https://abmedia.io/dydx-chain-v10-released/#dYdX_Chain_%E4%B8%8A%E7%B7%9A%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A3%E7%A2%BC%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E9%96%8B%E6%BA%90" title="dYdX Chain 上线，代码完全开源">dYdX Chain 上线，代码完全开源</a></li><li class="insert-page-1 insert-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2" href="https://abmedia.io/dydx-chain-v10-released/#dYdX_%E8%88%87_Uniswap_%E4%BA%92%E5%88%A5%E8%8B%97%E9%A0%AD%EF%BC%9F" title="dYdX 与 Uniswap 互别苗头？">dYdX 与 Uniswap 互别苗头？</a></li><li class="insert-page-1 insert-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3" href="https://abmedia.io/dydx-chain-v10-released/#dYdX_%E5%89%B5%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%BA%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%9F%E7%99%BC%E8%A8%80%EF%BC%9A%E8%87%B4%E6%95%AC_Fred_Ehrsam" title="dYdX 创办人近期发言：致敬 Fred Ehrsam">dYdX 创办人近期发言：致敬 Fred Ehrsam</a></li></ul></nav></div><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="dYdX_Chain_%E4%B8%8A%E7%B7%9A%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A3%E7%A2%BC%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E9%96%8B%E6%BA%90"></span><strong>dYdX Chain 上线，代码完全开源</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>据官方公告，dYdX Chain v1.0 版本已正式推出，包括协议、订单簿、前端等所有代码皆<a href="https://dydx.exchange/blog/dydx-chain-audit" target="_blank" rel="noopener">完成审计</a>，并且<a href="https://github.com/dydxprotocol" target="_blank" rel="noopener">全数开源</a>。</p><p>dYdX 强调了几点：</p><ol><li><p>可达到 2,000 TPS</p></li><li><p>完全去中心化，dYdX 不会运行任何基础设施</p></li><li><p>dYdX Chain 基础设施由全球 DeFi 爱好者运行</p></li></ol><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">1/ It’s finally here 🎉</p><p>Today, we’re proud to present and fully open-source the completed dYdX Chain!</p><p>This is the next chapter for dYdX and we’re so excited that it’s here.</p><p>Let’s get into the details:<a href="https://t.co/ydil2jkqJs">https://t.co/ydil2jkqJs</a></p><p>— dYdX (@dYdX) <a href="https://twitter.com/dYdX/status/1716802093946921353?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 24, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="dYdX_%E8%88%87_Uniswap_%E4%BA%92%E5%88%A5%E8%8B%97%E9%A0%AD%EF%BC%9F"></span><strong>dYdX 与 Uniswap 互别苗头？</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>不同于 Uniswap 为防范代码抄袭而采取了 BSL 商业许可证，dYdX Chain 宣布代码完全开源。</p><p>此外，就在创办人 Hayden Adams 宣布 Uniswap 将开始收取 0.15% 的前端手续费后，dYdX 创办人在几个小时内宣布，dYdX 将转型公共利益公司，不会从 V4 产生任何交易收入。</p><p><strong>(<a href="https://abmedia.io/dydx-becomes-a-public-benefit-corporation" target="_blank" rel="noopener">dYdX 转型成公共利益公司，不会从 V4 产生交易费收入！主网预计本月推出</a>)</strong></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">dYdX Trading Inc. has officially updated its charter to become a Public Benefit Corporation</p><p>As open source software developers, we will not operate or generate trading fee revenue from dYdX v4. We are serious about being as aligned as possible with the community 🤝</p><p>— Antonio | dYdX (@AntonioMJuliano) <a href="https://twitter.com/AntonioMJuliano/status/1714251418675155435?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 17, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="dYdX_%E5%89%B5%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%BA%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%9F%E7%99%BC%E8%A8%80%EF%BC%9A%E8%87%B4%E6%95%AC_Fred_Ehrsam"></span><strong>dYdX 创办人近期发言：致敬 Fred Ehrsam</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>Fred Ehrsam 日前宣布卸下 Paradigm 的执行合伙人职位，而 dYdX 创办人 Antonio Juliano 似乎因此有感而发。</p><p>他推文对 Fred Ehrsam 先后创办了 Coinbase、Paradigm 表达敬意，并认为 Fred Ehrsam 离开如此重要的职位肯定是一个很困难的决定。</p><p>Antonio Juliano 也是如此，他表示 dYdX 执行长是自己感到最快乐、最完美的工作，并对目前协议所建立的一切感到骄傲。</p><p><strong>注：社群、部分媒体似乎误以为 Antonio Juliano 可能离职。</strong></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">If I ever decide to step down as CEO of dYdX, do not congratulate me</p><p>A change is difficult but not itself significant. What I have built, what I let go, what I hold on to, and what I do next are what matters</p><p>Instead I would hope for your respect, sadness, appreciation, and…</p><p>— Antonio | dYdX (@AntonioMJuliano) <a href="https://twitter.com/AntonioMJuliano/status/1717116626963759134?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 25, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p>
]]>
