        <item>
            <title>
                <![CDATA[华尔街日报惹议，数据机构 Elliptic 澄清：严重夸大哈马斯加密捐款]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p class="intro_quote">分析机构 Elliptic 的数据被引用在华尔街日报的争议文章中，Elliptic 对此出面澄清，称该报导错误引用了数据，但即便如此，该文记者仍拒绝撤回报导，并在推特上捍衞立场。</p><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_57 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">内容目录</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/elliptic-counters-wsj-report#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-653a6a1fd026e"><span class=""><span style="display:none;">Toggle</span><span class="ez-toc-icon-toggle-span"><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="list-377408" width="20px" height="20px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999" class="arrow-unsorted-368013"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="10px" height="10px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.2" baseProfile="tiny"><path d="M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z"></path></svg></span></span></label><input aria-label="Toggle" type="checkbox" id="item-653a6a1fd026e"></a></span></div><nav><ul class="ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 "><li class="insert-page-1 insert-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1" href="https://abmedia.io/elliptic-counters-wsj-report/#%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%87%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%8B%E5%AF%A6%EF%BC%9F" title="华尔街日报是否夸大事实？">华尔街日报是否夸大事实？</a></li><li class="insert-page-1 insert-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2" href="https://abmedia.io/elliptic-counters-wsj-report/#Elliptic%EF%BC%9A%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1%E6%9C%89%E8%AA%A4" title="Elliptic：华尔街日报有误">Elliptic：华尔街日报有误</a></li><li class="insert-page-1 insert-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3" href="https://abmedia.io/elliptic-counters-wsj-report/#Elliptic%EF%BC%9A%E6%AD%A3%E8%88%87%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E8%80%85%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E9%87%90%E6%B8%85%E4%BA%8B%E5%AF%A6" title="Elliptic：正与相关者合作厘清事实">Elliptic：正与相关者合作厘清事实</a></li></ul></nav></div><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%87%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%8B%E5%AF%A6%EF%BC%9F"></span><strong>华尔街日报是否夸大事实？</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>之前华尔街日报曾报导「哈马斯相关加密钱包收到了 4,100 万美元」，这不仅让大众再次加深对加密货币的负面观感，同时也加重潜在监管压力，被反加密出名的参议员 Elizabeth Warren 用来趁势推动《数位资产反洗钱法案》。</p><p><strong>(<a href="https://abmedia.io/hamas-linked-crypto-accounts-frozen-by-israeli-police-with-help-of-binance" target="_blank" rel="noopener">以巴冲突持续，币安与以色列合作扣押哈马斯帐户，以断其金援</a>)</strong></p><p>Messari 创办人兼执行长 Ryan Selkis 就曾表示，哈马斯早发现加密货币具有可追溯性，并在四月份就已停止使用加密货币进行募款。</p><p><a href="https://www.elliptic.co/blog/setting-the-record-straight-on-crypto-crowdfunding-by-hamas" target="_blank" rel="noopener">加密分析机构 Elliptic</a> 在 10 月 25 日更以长文反驳华尔街日报。</p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Elliptic%EF%BC%9A%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1%E6%9C%89%E8%AA%A4"></span><strong>Elliptic：华尔街日报有误</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>华尔街日报在报导中引用了 Elliptic 的数据，称从 2021 年 8 月到今年 6 月，与圣战组织 (PIJ) 关联的钱包收到了高达 9,300 万美元的加密货币。</p><p>报导也引用另一机构 BitOK 的数据，称哈马斯相关钱包在同时期收到约 4,100 万美元。</p><p>Elliptic 对此澄清几点：</p><ol><li><p>10 月 7 日至今，哈马斯仅收到 21,000 美元加密货币，且火速遭冻结。</p></li><li><p>PIJ 钱包是「收到」了 9,300 万美元加密货币，绝对不代表他们募到这么多钱。</p></li><li><p>这些钱包也涉及交易所钱包，并无法确定资金是否皆属 PIJ 所有。</p></li></ol><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Elliptic%EF%BC%9A%E6%AD%A3%E8%88%87%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E8%80%85%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E9%87%90%E6%B8%85%E4%BA%8B%E5%AF%A6"></span><strong>Elliptic：正与相关者合作厘清事实</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>Elliptic 表示正与参议员 Elizabeth Warren 的代表、华尔街日报作者交涉，以澄清事实。</p><p>不过该篇文章的记者 Ian Talley 似乎非常坚持最初的报导，即便众多加密社群向他呼吁立即撤回报导，他仍持续在推文中引用能支持他论点的数据。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">"Digital-currency wallets that Israeli authorities linked to the PIJ received as much as $93 million in crypto between August 2021 and June this year, analysis by leading crypto researcher Elliptic showed."</p><p>"It couldn’t be determined whether the crypto they received was directly…</p><p>— Ian Talley (@IanTalley) <a href="https://twitter.com/IanTalley/status/1717300164635906282?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 25, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p>
]]>
            </description>
